<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{definitionNm}} — Station8 Subway Map</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design.css">
</head>
<body>
{{> _nav }}

<div class="swe-container" style="padding-top: var(--space-xxl); padding-bottom: var(--space-section);">

    <div class="swe-flex-between swe-mb-xl">
        <div>
            <a href="/line/definitions" class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 13px;">← Lines</a>
            <h1 class="swe-display-lg" style="margin: var(--space-xs) 0 0;">{{definitionNm}}</h1>
            <p class="swe-body-md swe-mute" style="margin: var(--space-sm) 0 0;">
                v{{versionNo}} · {{nodeCount}} 역 · {{edgeCount}} 트랙
                {{#description}} · {{description}}{{/description}}
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="swe-row">
            <a href="/line/definitions" class="swe-btn-tertiary">Back</a>
            <a href="/line/builder" class="swe-btn-primary">+ New Line</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="swe-subway-frame">
        <div id="subway-map"></div>
    </div>

    <p class="swe-caption-sm" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
        ※ 정적 미리보기 (M1). 인스턴스 진행 위치 오버레이는 후속 작업(M2)에서.
    </p>

</div>

<script id="graph-data" type="application/json">{{{graphJson}}}</script>
<script src="/js/subway-map.js"></script>
<script>
(function () {
    const raw = document.getElementById('graph-data').textContent;
    const graph = JSON.parse(raw);
    Station8SubwayMap.render(document.getElementById('subway-map'), graph);
})();
</script>
</body>
</html>
